{"id":1104,"date":"2025-04-05T00:19:58","date_gmt":"2025-04-04T17:19:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1104"},"modified":"2025-12-14T10:17:49","modified_gmt":"2025-12-14T03:17:49","slug":"lan-kim-phi-kim-mun-san","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/lan-kim-phi-kim-mun-san\/","title":{"rendered":"L\u0103n kim phi kim m\u1ee5n s\u1ea7n"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p cho m\u1ee5n s\u1ea9n vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng, m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to, s\u1eb9o r\u1ed7 sau tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>K\u00edch th\u00edch t\u0103ng sinh qua tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o gi\u00fap b\u1ea1t s\u1eebng gi\u1ea3m b\u00edt t\u1eafc, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n.<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1, gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e2m do m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<\/li>\n<li>Th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee5n, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>V\u1edbi c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf t\u1ea1o t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1ea3 tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0o s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong da, ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 k\u00edch th\u00edch c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng sinh collagen v\u00e0 elastin gi\u00fap t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng k\u00e9p \u0111\u00e0o th\u1ea3i nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n nhanh &amp; t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n.<\/li>\n<li>T\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c m\u1ee5n ch\u1ee9a Retinol, Sulfur, Bakuchiol, AHA, BHA v\u00e0 c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ng sinh th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt gi\u00fap k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi, t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng tr\u00ean da v\u00e0 gom c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n s\u1ea9n vi\u00eam k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m duy tr\u00ec &#8211; ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n m\u1edbi.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 01 ti\u1ebfng.<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 03 &#8211; 04 bu\u1ed5i, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb 21 &#8211; 30 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -8px; top: 416.241px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p cho m\u1ee5n s\u1ea9n vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng, m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to, s\u1eb9o r\u1ed7 sau tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3571,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[34],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1104","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-microneedling","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1104","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1104"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gs